launcher.name: Sky Factory
launcher.description:
Calling this pack modded skyblock is like calling the Bat Mobile a "car". It's skyblock, but like you've never seen it before! High tech mods, full automation, and spawning in the void with nothing but a tree and a *single* piece of dirt between you and certain death!

Have questions? Ask the current maintainer and dev: twitch.tv/darkosto or twitter.com/darkostoTV
